chart.name: Total Disk I/O Ops
chart.programText:
A = data('disk_ops.write', filter=filter('plugin', 'disk') and (not filter('agent', '*'))).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('disk_ops.read', filter=filter('plugin', 'disk') and (not filter('agent', '*'))).sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: CPU %
chart.programText:
A = data('cpu.utilization', filter=filter('plugin', 'signalfx-metadata') and (not filter('agent', '*'))).mean(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).max().publish(label='B')
C = (A).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')

chart.name: Network I/O

chart.name: Memory Used %

chart.name: Top CPU %

chart.name: Network Errors
